menu "Yamada Custom Android Drivers"

config OCHINAI_INAHO_AUDIO
    tristate "Ochinai Inaho Audio — SCHED_FIFO + PM QoS + CPUSet tuning"
    depends on CPU_FREQ && SCHED_DEBUG
    help
      Boosts audio threads to SCHED_FIFO priority, locks CPU latency
      via PM QoS, and expands CPUSet for audio processes to include
      all cores. Author: Kanagawa Yamada. Say Y or M.

config SPARXIE_SWAP_TUNER
	tristate "Tune the swappiness value"
	help
	  Change the value of the swappiness, by this I make it 30 check
	  using cat /proc/sys/vm/swappiness

config RACO_RC_OVERRIDE
    bool "Raco Override Universal .rc Override API"
    default y
    help 
	  To counter the sysfs write by rogue vendor init.rc scripts during boot.

config PAVOLIA_REINE_RESETPROP
	tristate "Pavolia Reine API resetprop tool"
	depends on KSU
	default y
	help
	  Please see the required SELinux for this (See selinux.sh for more details)

config SANDEVISTAN_BOOT
    tristate "Sandevistan Boot — temporary performance governor boost"
    depends on CPU_FREQ && CPU_FREQ_GOV_PERFORMANCE && CPU_FREQ_GOV_SCHEDUTIL
    help
      Sets the CPUfreq governor to 'performance' during boot for
      BOOST_DELAY_SEC seconds, then reverts to 'schedutil'.

config YAMADA_GAMING_BOOST
    tristate "Yamada Gaming Boost — CPU input boost + schedutil tuning"
    depends on CPU_FREQ && CPU_FREQ_GOV_SCHEDUTIL && INPUT
    help
      Boosts CPU to max frequency and sets schedutil rate_limit_us
      to 0 on touch/key input events. Reverts after boost window.
      Author: Kanagawa Yamada. Say Y or M.

config YAMADA_TENEBRION
    tristate "Tenebrion — CPU freq drop on screen off"
    depends on CPU_FREQ && SUSPEND
    help
      Drops all CPU frequencies to minimum on system suspend,
      restores full range on resume.
      Author: Kanagawa Yamada. Say Y or M.

config SCHEDUTIL_ENFORCER
	tristate "Enforce Schedutil as Default Governor"
	depends on CPU_FREQ_DEFAULT_GOV_SCHEDUTIL && RACO_RC_OVERRIDE
	help
    This have to be done because some init on vendor sets the Governor
    to sugov_ext (Which actually kinda same with schedutil). But because
    my eye I don't want to see it. Feel free to use this as reference if
    you want to change the governor with your own choice. Say Y or N

config YAMADA_DEV_IDENTIFICATION
  tristate "Identification of this kernel developer IS"
  depends on PAVOLIA_REINE_RESETPROP
  help
    This is actually to test PAVOLIA_REINE_SETPROP but eh, it would be a
    good Identification that this kernel is make by me anyway. This will
    be also an example usage of PAVOLIA_REINE_SETPROP API

config AYUNDA_RISU_SAFEPROP
  tristate "Spoof some props for reduced root detection"
  depends on PAVOLIA_REINE_RESETPROP
  help
    Set some props using resetprop in order to fix some detection. This
    However not magically gives your device locked state, spoof basic
    Google integrity, this only help reduce detection of banking apps 
    on your devices

config AMBATUBANK
  tristate "Stop Fcking Detect My Root Devices!"
  depends on KSU_SUSFS 
  help
    This has to be done because banking app detects root. Fk them, I just
    want to root my device because I want to game with higher perfromance
    not hacking to your bank accounts! I ain't a criminal to do that!

endmenu
